بَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":172,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/172.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/172.mp3"],"text":"وَمِنَ ٱلنَّاسِ مَن يَتَّخِذُ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ أَندَادًۭا يُحِبُّونَهُمْ كَحُبِّ ٱللَّهِ ۖ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ أَشَدُّ حُبًّۭا لِّلَّهِ ۗ وَلَوْ يَرَى ٱلَّذِينَ ظَلَمُوٓا۟ إِذْ يَرَوْنَ ٱلْعَذَابَ أَنَّ ٱلْقُوَّةَ لِلَّهِ جَمِيعًۭا وَأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ شَدِيدُ ٱلْعَذَابِ","numberInSurah":165,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":25,"ruku":21,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":173,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/173.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/173.mp3"],"text":"إِذْ تَبَرَّأَ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتُّبِعُوا۟ مِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّبَعُوا۟ وَرَأَوُا۟ ٱلْعَذَابَ وَتَقَطَّعَتْ بِهِمُ ٱلْأَسْبَابُ","numberInSurah":166,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":25,"ruku":21,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":174,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/174.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/174.mp3"],"text":"وَقَالَ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّبَعُوا۟ لَوْ أَنَّ لَنَا كَرَّةًۭ فَنَتَبَرَّأَ مِنْهُمْ كَمَا تَبَرَّءُوا۟ مِنَّا ۗ كَذَٰلِكَ يُرِيهِمُ ٱللَّهُ أَعْمَٰلَهُمْ حَسَرَٰتٍ عَلَيْهِمْ ۖ وَمَا هُم بِخَٰرِجِينَ مِنَ ٱلنَّارِ","numberInSurah":167,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":25,"ruku":21,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":175,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/175.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/175.mp3"],"text":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ كُلُوا۟ مِمَّا فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ حَلَٰلًۭا طَيِّبًۭا وَلَا تَتَّبِعُوا۟ خُطُوَٰتِ ٱلشَّيْطَٰنِ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ لَكُمْ عَدُوٌّۭ مُّبِينٌ","numberInSurah":168,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":25,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":176,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/176.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/176.mp3"],"text":"إِنَّمَا يَأْمُرُكُم بِٱلسُّوٓءِ وَٱلْفَحْشَآءِ وَأَن تَقُولُوا۟ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ مَا لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","numberInSurah":169,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":25,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":177,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/177.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/177.mp3"],"text":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱتَّبِعُوا۟ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ قَالُوا۟ بَلْ نَتَّبِعُ مَآ أَلْفَيْنَا عَلَيْهِ ءَابَآءَنَآ ۗ أَوَلَوْ كَانَ ءَابَآؤُهُمْ لَا يَعْقِلُونَ شَيْـًۭٔا وَلَا يَهْتَدُونَ","numberInSurah":170,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":178,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/178.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/178.mp3"],"text":"وَمَثَلُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ كَمَثَلِ ٱلَّذِى يَنْعِقُ بِمَا لَا يَسْمَعُ إِلَّا دُعَآءًۭ وَنِدَآءًۭ ۚ صُمٌّۢ بُكْمٌ عُمْىٌۭ فَهُمْ لَا يَعْقِلُونَ","numberInSurah":171,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":179,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/179.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/179.mp3"],"text":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ كُلُوا۟ مِن طَيِّبَٰتِ مَا رَزَقْنَٰكُمْ وَٱشْكُرُوا۟ لِلَّهِ إِن كُنتُمْ إِيَّاهُ تَعْبُدُونَ","numberInSurah":172,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":180,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/180.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/180.mp3"],"text":"إِنَّمَا حَرَّمَ عَلَيْكُمُ ٱلْمَيْتَةَ وَٱلدَّمَ وَلَحْمَ ٱلْخِنزِيرِ وَمَآ أُهِلَّ بِهِۦ لِغَيْرِ ٱللَّهِ ۖ فَمَنِ ٱضْطُرَّ غَيْرَ بَاغٍۢ وَلَا عَادٍۢ فَلَآ إِثْمَ عَلَيْهِ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ غَفُورٌۭ رَّحِيمٌ","numberInSurah":173,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":181,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/181.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/181.mp3"],"text":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَكْتُمُونَ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ مِنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَيَشْتَرُونَ بِهِۦ ثَمَنًۭا قَلِيلًا ۙ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ مَا يَأْكُلُونَ فِى بُطُونِهِمْ إِلَّا ٱلنَّارَ وَلَا يُكَلِّمُهُمُ ٱللَّهُ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ وَلَا يُزَكِّيهِمْ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ","numberInSurah":174,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":182,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/182.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/182.mp3"],"text":"أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱشْتَرَوُا۟ ٱلضَّلَٰلَةَ بِٱلْهُدَىٰ وَٱلْعَذَابَ بِٱلْمَغْفِرَةِ ۚ فَمَآ أَصْبَرَهُمْ عَلَى ٱلنَّارِ","numberInSurah":175,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},{"number":183,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/183.mp3","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/183.mp3"],"text":"ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ نَزَّلَ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۗ وَإِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱخْتَلَفُوا۟ فِى ٱلْكِتَٰبِ لَفِى شِقَاقٍۭ بَعِيدٍۢ","numberInSurah":176,"juz":2,"manzil":1,"page":26,"ruku":22,"hizbQuarter":10,"sajda":false,"surah":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}}],"surahs":{"2":{"number":2,"name":"سُورَةُ البَقَرَةِ","englishName":"Al-Baqara","englishNameTranslation":"The Cow","revelationType":"Medinan"}},"edition":{}}}